overview: Home alone on a Friday night, Donnie (Donnie Rock) tries out a new Genie App on his phone. Low-and-behold, a beautiful Genie (La Sirena 69) appears! The voluptuous Genie grants her new master 3 wishes: first, a sexy "20 something" brunette (Jennifer White) and then, both master and horny magical Genie make their wildest wishes come true! (Bella Rolland, Krissy Lynn, Ramon Nomar).
title: Genie Wishes 2
